Data Source & Beneficiary of Product
========================================================
**Source of Data**

<font size="6">
* CO<sub>2</sub> Dataset : Our World in Data (https://ourworldindata.org/co2-emissions) and  Global Carbon Project.
* Global Temperature Dataset: Global Climate Change (https://climate.nasa.gov/vital-signs/global-temperature/).
* Mean Sea Level Dataset	: sea-level-rise (https://github.com/datasets/sea-level-rise).	
</font size> 


**Beneficiary of Product**

<b>General Public:</b>
- Insights on carbon emission can provide and promote environmental awareness to the public 

<b>Government(s) and global health organization(s):</b>
- Insights on carbon emission can be utilized in the implementation of global climate initiatives


